title: Poppin' Boxes With Windsor James
description:
**The contest is over but thank you to everyone for joining.

Wanna pop boxes like a pro? Well then go LIKE us on the KR3W Facebook page and enter yourself in the "Poppin' Boxes" contest to win this big ass box of KR3W gear that Windsor James just packed up for you. Entry is free and open to anyone who is a fan of KR3W on Facebook. Winner will be selected at random. Do it. Now. http://a.pgtb.me/h8hhQb
